#: ../../tinylang-spec.md:3
msgid ""
"TinyLang is a minimal demo markup language designed to showcase how to "
"add language support to lang-check. It is intentionally trivial — just "
"complex enough to demonstrate prose extraction, math exclusion, and "
"structural commands."
msgstr ""

